<h1>Example Runner</h1>

<ul>
    <li>The filename is important, should be all lowercase and spaces become hyphens, so <b>Jin Furai</b> becomes <b>jin-furai</b>. This is called the "slug."</li>
    <li>The file extension is <b>.md</b>, so it becomes <b>jin-furai.md</b>.</li>
    <li>The filename (slug) will be used when entering a run that references this runner.</li>
    <li>Then in the file, use the formatting below.</li>
    <li><b>title</b>: This is the (nick) name</li>
    <li><b>twitter</b>, <b>youtube</b>, <b>twitch</b>, <b>patreon</b>: Enter full URLs (with https://), or leave empty if you don't have it.</li>
    <li><b>country</b>: A two-letter country code for the country you wanna represent. It's a fun thing. Leave empty if you do not want a flag next to your name.</li>
    <li><b>weapons</b>: This runner will be shown on the <a href="/runners/">Weapon Masters</a> section. Below are all weapon options. Delete the weapons that are not relevant.</li>
</ul>

